description.narrative:
Since the first annual report is yet to come in march of 2022, specific results has not been reported. However the inception report and follow up meetings with Oxfam during the field trip to Erbil and Mosul in Dec. 2021 has concluded the following;

- Oxfam works through two different implementing partner organisations; Al Ghad (partner that focus on Social Cohesion) and Sewan (partner that focus on gender), two partners that where identified and chosen during the inception period of this project. 

- The project has started different educational programmes within both agribusiness but also in normative dialogue. Sida visited classes within these course in Mosul in December 2021. The activities made a valid impression and Oxfam seemed to have found suitable implementing partners as well as participants to the courses at hand. Attendees on these courses expressed that they where satisfied with the curriculum and seemed to value what they where taught within them.
